longBusinessSummary: Winsome Yarns Limited engages in the textile business in India and internationally. The company manufactures and sells yarns and knitwear. The company offers products made of natural, man-made, and other fiber materials. It markets its products in Europe, Australia, America, Asia, and Africa. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Chandigarh, India.
